reviews.review_text:
First song is missing If you want your Uncle, liste to it here http://www.archive.org/details/gd73-12-08.sbd.gustin.1811.sbeok.shnf then come back for the rest of this great show!
Peace, Bob

You know better, but I know him... This is in my opinion some of the most mellow and beautiful sounding Grateful Dead music.
The vocals are so fine from this era and the playing tends to be lighter than air.
"Nothings gonna bring him back"
